<D>__{are you tim? tim lippe?}
<A>__{tim just smiles a wide, deer in headlights smile.}
<C>__{black man }
<D>__{i'm ronald wilkes. bill krogstad said we were gonna be roommates?}
<A>__{ronald wilkes, 45, is conservative in dress and demeanor.}
<C>__{millie }
<D>__{tim! tim! tiiim!}
<C>__{tim}
<P>__{(into phone)}
<D>__{let me call you back, mil.}
<A>__{tim clicks off his phone, just stares at ronald.}
<C>__{ronald}
<D>__{you are tim...?}
<C>__{tim}
<D>__{um. yeah. yes. you bet. for a minute there i was like, whoa, i'm gonna be robbed here, or...}
<A>__{tim laughs loudly. ronald just looks at tim. a beat.}
